snippet.title: Cave Digger Trailer: Railway into the Depths
snippet.description:
Join our Discord community discord.gg/cavedigger
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
NEW UPDATE - Railway into the Depths

In this massive content update you, the miner, are unbound from the elevator and are free to explore the world of Cave Digger on a bigger scale. The word about the riches beneath the surface has spread and old mining tunnels have been discovered in the town.

Fix and update the train to enter the mines and dig deeper than any miner before you! Bring wealth to the town and see how the economy booms!

Available at  Oculus Quest, PlayStation, Oculus, Steam and HTC stores
